title: Whose Zeit Are You On 9/4: Mulan, Celtics, Jessica Krug, Wendy Bell, Jay Cutler/Tomi Lahren

description:
On this edition of Whose Zeit Are You On Jack and DJ Danl discuss the new Mulan film coming out and the controversy surrounding it, the Celtics loss to the Raptors with a Buzzer-Beater 3, another white woman pretending to be Black is exposed, Wendy Bell is fired after saying protesters should be shot at National monuments, and Jay Cutler is dating Tomi Lahren.
